description: Philip Manshaus appears in court in Oslo accused of shooting his sister before attacking a mosque.
title: Norway mosque attack and murder trial begins in Oslo
title_page: Norway mosque attack and murder trial begins in Oslo - BBC News
maintext: The 22-year-old has admitted then taking a number of guns to the Al-Noor mosque in Baerum, near his home. Three people were inside at the time, who managed to overpower him.
